tinct_date            = 21 October 2017\n| extinct_title = Merged into [[:ee:R\u00f5uge vald|expanded R\u00f5uge Parish]]\n| subdivision_type        = [[List of sovereign states|Country]]\n| subdivision_name        = [[File:Flag of Estonia.svg|25px]]  [[Estonia]]\n| subdivision_type1       = [[Counties of Estonia|County]]\n| subdivision_name1       = [[File:V\u00f5rumaa lipp.svg|25px]] [[V\u00f5ru County]]\n| seat_type               = Administrative centre\n| seat                    = [[R\u00f5uge]]\n| leader_party            = \n| leader_title            = \n| leader_name             = \n| area_total_km2          = 263.7\n| population_total        = 2045\n| population_as_of        = 01.01.2006\n| population_density_km2  = auto\n| website                 = [http://www.rauge.ee www.rauge.ee]\n}}\n\n'''R\u00f5uge Parish''' ({{lang-et|R\u00f5uge vald}}; {{lang-vro|R\u00f5ug\u00f5 vald}}) is a rural [[Municipalities of Estonia|municipality]] of [[Estonia]], in [[V\u00f5ru County]]. In 2006, it had a population of 2,045 and an area of 263.7&nbsp;km\u00b2.\n\nIn 2017, it merged with [[Haanja Parish]], [[M\u00f5niste Parish]], [[Misso Parish]], and [[Varstu Parish]] to create a new entity. It retained the R\u00f5uge Parish name.\n\n==Settlements==\n;small boroughs\n[[Misso]] - [[R\u00f5uge]] - [[Varstu]]\n;Villages\n[[Aabra]] - [[Ahitsa]] - [[Ala-Palo]] - [[Ala-Suhka]] - [[Ala-Tilga]] - [[Andsum\u00e4e]] - [[Augli]] - [[Haabsilla]] - [[Haanja]] - [[H\u00e4\u00e4rm\u00e4ni]] - [[Haavistu]] - [[Haki, Estonia|Haki]] - [[Hallim\u00e4e]] - [[H\u00e4mkoti]] - [[Handimiku]] - [[Hanija]] - [[Hansi, Estonia|Hansi]] - [[Hapsu]] - [[H\u00e4r\u00e4m\u00e4e]] - [[Harjuk\u00fcla]] - [[Heedu]] - [[Heibri]] - [[Hinsa]] - [[Hino, V\u00f5ru County|Hino]] - [[Hintsiko]] - [[Hinu]] - [[Holdi, R\u00f5uge Parish|Holdi]] - [[Horoski]] - [[Horosuu]] - [[Horsa, Estonia|Horsa]] - [[Hot\u00f5m\u00e4e]] - [[Hulaku]] - [[Hurda, R\u00f5uge Parish|Hurda]] - [[H\u00fcrova]] - [[H\u00fcrsi]] - [[H\u00fcti